com.skilltradiez.skilltraderz

Class TradeIdIsNullException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • com.skilltradiez.skilltraderz.TradeIdIsNullException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class TradeIdIsNullException
extends java.lang.Exception
    Suppose a Trade ID Object is being looked for by application, if it doesn't exist or returns null then we have a large problem that can easily crash numerous parts of our application. Null pointer exceptions aren't fun to deal with. This exception was specially crafted to take into account the possibility that there may be a time when we have a Trade ID equal to null appear- and we want to handle it with grace.
